[This confirms the suspicion existing for some time on the source for
the 2 strains being the same. Clearly the German case in Aachen scored
himself some heroin with or without the shipper knowing. Hopefully it
was just for him and not sufficient to be shared with others. In that
a month has passed without new German cases it would be logical to
think that the German case will be singular. - Mod.MHJ]

